Name:		lame
Version:	3.96.1
Release:	2
License:	GPL
Group:		Applications/Sound
Source0:	http://dl.sourceforge.net/lame/%{name}-%{version}.tar.gz
# Source0-md5:	e1206c46a5e276feca11a7149e2fc6ac
